%F A000531 a(n-1) = 4^n*sum_{k=0..n} binomial(2*k+1, k)*4^(-k) = (2*n+1)*(2*n+3)*C(n) - 2^(2*n+1) (C(n) = Catalan); g.f.: x*c(x)/(1-4*x)^(3/2), c(x): g.f. of Catalan numbers A000108. - _Wolfdieter Lang_
